qnapi: qnapi (Qt subtitle downloader)
qnapi:
qnapi: QNapi is a Qt application for finding and downloading subtitles for
qnapi: movie files. It can use subtitle databases such as NapiProjekt,
qnapi: OpenSubtitles, and Napisy24, and it provides both graphical and
qnapi: command-line interfaces.
qnapi:
qnapi: It can scan directories for movies, download matched subtitles, and
qnapi: convert subtitles between common formats.
qnapi:
qnapi: Homepage: https://qnapi.github.io/
